ATTRIBUTION
    If you use Mars (code), the benchmark (data), or the results, please cite
    the work — see CITATION.cff.

THIRD-PARTY SYSTEMS
    Mars consumes Cortex (memory/retrieval), AutoDev (agent execution), and
    reserves extension points for Sentinel (governance). These are separate
    systems; only their PROVIDER INTERFACES and mock implementations are included
    here. The real Cortex/AutoDev implementations are not part of this release.

NO CREDENTIALS
    This repository contains no API keys, tokens, or service endpoints.
    Reproduction that requires external services (e.g. Voyage embeddings, a real
    AutoDev MCP server) reads them from environment variables documented in the
    reports; the offline tier (committed cache) requires none.
